  "detailed_description": "<i>\"The Boomer Slayers come to purge the world of filth and bring masculinity and brutality back to society\"</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746760/extras/9d8e13a0d5c68d30f54216c36e3a099a.poster.avif?t=1656343930\" width=620 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746760/extras/9d8e13a0d5c68d30f54216c36e3a099a.webm?t=1656343930\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746760/extras/9d8e13a0d5c68d30f54216c36e3a099a.mp4?t=1656343930\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>BOOMER SLAYERS is an indie game by a single developer. It is a mix of an old-school hardcore gameplay and modern low-poly looks with boomer humor.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746760/extras/ebe2e652f4de394ea43a0d0d32e2408a.poster.avif?t=1656343930\" width=620 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746760/extras/ebe2e652f4de394ea43a0d0d32e2408a.webm?t=1656343930\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746760/extras/ebe2e652f4de394ea43a0d0d32e2408a.mp4?t=1656343930\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Use your BADASS character to clear The Building by using brute force! Use your JUSTICE PUNSH to interact with enemies and environment.<br></li><li>Upgrade your S-KILLS to own your enemies with style!<br></li><li>Use MONETOS to buy stylish colors for your hero!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746760/extras/8ed6aed8e381181e3b272d09edfc042a.poster.avif?t=1656343930\" width=620 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746760/extras/8ed6aed8e381181e3b272d09edfc042a.webm?t=1656343930\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746760/extras/8ed6aed8e381181e3b272d09edfc042a.mp4?t=1656343930\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Play with your badass friends in local co-op mode!<br>Try to do your best not to die of laughter.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746760/extras/4142e7528ffa76d21263ab6808acd729.poster.avif?t=1656343930\" width=620 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746760/extras/4142e7528ffa76d21263ab6808acd729.webm?t=1656343930\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746760/extras/4142e7528ffa76d21263ab6808acd729.mp4?t=1656343930\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>When you're ready, switch from GAME JOURNALIST DIFFICULTY to NORMAL (or even VERY NORMAL) and test your might in a REAL CHALLENGE. Slay your enemies LIKE A BOSS!<br><br>(Some in-game jokes may be understandable only to native Russians)</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<i>\"The Boomer Slayers come to purge the world of filth and bring masculinity and brutality back to society\"</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746760/extras/9d8e13a0d5c68d30f54216c36e3a099a.poster.avif?t=1656343930\" width=620 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746760/extras/9d8e13a0d5c68d30f54216c36e3a099a.webm?t=1656343930\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746760/extras/9d8e13a0d5c68d30f54216c36e3a099a.mp4?t=1656343930\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>BOOMER SLAYERS is an indie game by a single developer. It is a mix of an old-school hardcore gameplay and modern low-poly looks with boomer humor.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746760/extras/ebe2e652f4de394ea43a0d0d32e2408a.poster.avif?t=1656343930\" width=620 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746760/extras/ebe2e652f4de394ea43a0d0d32e2408a.webm?t=1656343930\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746760/extras/ebe2e652f4de394ea43a0d0d32e2408a.mp4?t=1656343930\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Use your BADASS character to clear The Building by using brute force! Use your JUSTICE PUNSH to interact with enemies and environment.<br></li><li>Upgrade your S-KILLS to own your enemies with style!<br></li><li>Use MONETOS to buy stylish colors for your hero!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746760/extras/8ed6aed8e381181e3b272d09edfc042a.poster.avif?t=1656343930\" width=620 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746760/extras/8ed6aed8e381181e3b272d09edfc042a.webm?t=1656343930\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746760/extras/8ed6aed8e381181e3b272d09edfc042a.mp4?t=1656343930\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Play with your badass friends in local co-op mode!<br>Try to do your best not to die of laughter.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746760/extras/4142e7528ffa76d21263ab6808acd729.poster.avif?t=1656343930\" width=620 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746760/extras/4142e7528ffa76d21263ab6808acd729.webm?t=1656343930\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746760/extras/4142e7528ffa76d21263ab6808acd729.mp4?t=1656343930\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>When you're ready, switch from GAME JOURNALIST DIFFICULTY to NORMAL (or even VERY NORMAL) and test your might in a REAL CHALLENGE. Slay your enemies LIKE A BOSS!<br><br>(Some in-game jokes may be understandable only to native Russians)</li></ul>",
